What you need to know:

Kulusevski, who has had a meteoric rise in Serie A with Juventus, and Isak, another 21-year-old prodigy from Real Sociedad, will both be making their first appearances at the European ChampionshipAnother young new asset to the team is forward Jordan Larsson, who after a strong season with Spartak Moscow will have big shoes to fill, taking the position left open by IbrahimovicHowever, the team will not just consist of greenhorns and will be able to rely on the experience of more seasoned players like Marcus Berg